JDK
Java Development Kit
It implements the Java Language and the Java Virtual Machine Specification and provides the Standard Edition of th Java Application Programming Interfece.

JDK can be installed on the following platforms:
- Microsoft Windows
- Linux
- MacOS

-------------------------
JVM
Java Virtual Machine
it is a software, enables a computer to run Java programs, as well as programs written in other languages that are also compiled to Java byte code
JVM contains JIT compiler(Just In Time Compiler), whose job is to translate byte code into os specific machine code
